n\r\n								<p><strong>INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY OWNERSHIP & USE</strong></p>\r\n								<p>The entire content of the Website, including all copyright, trademarks and other intellectual property rights it contains, including the use of the name ‘Aidan and Ice’ is the sole property of Aidan and Ice. All intellectual property rights in the Products (subject to the rights of any third party) belong Aidan and Ice.</p>\r\n								<p>This Site is for your personal non-commercial use only. You may not modify, copy, distribute, transmit, display, perform, reproduce, publish, license, commercially exploit, create derivative works from, transfer, data mine or sell any Content, software, products, or services contained within this Site. You may not use this Site, or any of its Content, to further any commercial purpose, including any advertising or advertising revenue generation activity on your own Site.</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>OUR RIGHTS TO CANCEL</strong></p>\r\n								<p>We reserve the right to cancel your order if: One or more of the Products you ordered was listed at an incorrect price due to a typographical error in the pricing information received by us from our suppliers or for any other reason. A Force Majeure Event occurs. If we do cancel your order we will notify you by e-mail. We are not be obliged to offer any additional compensation for disappointment suffered and we have no liability to you for any loss, damage, costs, expenses or other claims that you may incur. By shopping at www.aidanandice.com you agree with our policy and acknowledge our cancelation policy.</p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (14,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,9,'','','T&C 2',0,'','GIFT CARD','','<p><strong>Redemption</strong></p>\r\n								<p>Aidan and Ice Gift Cards (\"Gift Cards\") may only be redeemed toward the purchase of eligible goods and services provided by Aidan and Ice. Redemption of Gift Cards is subject to change in our sole discretion. Gift Cards include any Aidan and Ice Gift Cards you purchase that are automatically added to your Aidan and Ice Balance when you input the code. Your Aidan and Ice Balance displays the total remaining balance of all Gift Cards that have been applied to your Aidan and Ice account but not yet applied to a purchase. We may refer to your Aidan and Ice Balance as your “Gift Card balance”. Purchases are deducted from your Aidan and Ice Balance. Any unused Aidan and Ice Balance will remain associated with your Aidan and Ice account. If a purchase exceeds your Aidan and Ice Balance, the remaining amount must be paid with another payment method. To view your Aidan and Ice Balance, visit Your Account on Aidan and Ice. No fees apply to Gift Cards.</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>Limitations</strong></p>\r\n								<p>Neither your Aidan and Ice Balance nor your Gift Cards may be applied to the purchase of products at Aidan and Ice. Your Aidan and Ice Balance cannot be used to purchase other gift cards. Gift Cards cannot be reloaded, resold, transferred for value or redeemed for cash, except to the extent required by law. No portion of your Aidan and Ice Balance may be transferred to another Aidan and Ice account.</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>Risk of Loss</strong></p>\r\n								<p>The risk of loss and title for Gift Cards pass to the purchaser upon our electronic transmission of the Gift Card to the purchaser or designated recipient, or our delivery to the carrier, whichever is applicable. We are not responsible if any Gift Card is lost, stolen or destroyed or your Aidan and Ice Balance or any Gift Card is used without your permission.</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>Use of Aidan and Ice Balance or any Gift Card in Violation of these Terms and Conditions</strong></p>\r\n								<p>We reserve the right to void Gift Cards or any other component of your Aidan and Ice Balance, close customer accounts and bill alternative forms of payment if we suspect that a Gift Card is obtained, used or applied to an Aidan and Ice account (or your Aidan and Ice Balance is applied to a purchase) fraudulently, unlawfully or otherwise in violation of these terms and conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>General Terms</strong></p>\r\n								<p>The Aidan and Ice Conditions of Use apply. When you purchase, receive or apply a Gift Card to your account or your Aidan and Ice Balance to a purchase, you agree that the laws of Indonesia, without regard to principles of conflict of laws, will govern these terms and conditions and any dispute that may arise between you and Aidan and Ice, and its affiliates related to your use of a Gift Card or your Aidan and Ice Balance. We reserve the right to change these terms and conditions from time to time in our discretion. All terms and conditions are applicable to the extent permitted by law. If any of these terms and conditions are deemed invalid, void, or for any reason unenforceable, that unenforceable term will be deemed severable and will not affect the validity and enforceability of any remaining terms and conditions</p>\r\n\r\n								<p><strong>Balance Expiration</strong></p>\r\n								<p>The portion of your Aidan and Ice Balance made up of Gift Cards issued after will expire after 1 YEAR AFTER PURCHASE and may be applied to your Aidan and Ice account and applied to eligible purchases despite any stated expiration date.</p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (15,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,9,'','','T&C 3',0,'','PAYMENT OPTIONS','','<p><strong>BY TRANSFER</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Please kindly transfer, make sure the orders and delivery address is correct.</li>\r\n<li>After you made the transfer, please let us know by filling in the confirmation page.</li>\r\n<li>Fill in the order ID, Total payment, proofof transfer file (image) and click Submit!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BY CREDIT CARD (VISA / MASTER)</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Delivery Confirmation (We will let you know once your order has DISPATCHED by email!)  </li>\r\n<li>We will provide the tracking code. Delivery takes up to 3-14 business days, if we do not stated otherwise.</li>\r\n</ul>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (16,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,9,'','','T&C 4',0,'','PRESS','','<p>Contact our press officer at hello@aidanandice.com for any press requests.</p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (17,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,9,'','','T&C 5',0,'','DELIVERY','','<p>Aidan and Ice reserves the right to restrict the delivery of Products to certain areas. We will take all reasonable steps to deliver your order to you.</p>\r\n<p>Product is shipped into Aidan and Ice packaging. Delivery will be made to the address specified in the ORDER CONFIRMATION. Please also note that the shipping rates for many items we sell are weight-based. The weight of any such item can be found on its detail page.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Delivery Timing and Confirmation</strong></p>\r\n<p>The time for delivery of the Products shall not be of the essence of the contract. Delivery normally takes 1-14 business days, if not state otherwise. We will let you know once your order has dispatched by email! We will provide the tracking code.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** Delays If delays occur due to any reason, Aidan and Ice does not warrant or guarantee the delivery date and shall have no liability to you for any loss, damage, costs, expenses or other claims that you may incur as a result of late delivery</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Delivery Service Provided:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Within Jakarta: Gojek (IDR 25.000)</p>\r\n<p>Within Indonesia: JNE (IDR 50.000)</p>\r\n<p>International Delivery: DHL (Depends on the country)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>** IMPORTANT: IF DAMAGES OR ANY LOSSES OCCUR DURING DELIVERY, AIDAN AND ICE WILL NOT TAKE ANY RESPONSIBILITY.</strong></p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (18,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,9,'','','T&C 6',0,'','CUSTOM ORDER','','<p>We also specialize in custom-made pieces through Aidan and Ice Atelier. Through our personalized approach, we will thrive to make your dream piece into reality, whether you are looking for a custom-made piece for your special occasion or a special piece as a gift. At Aidan and Ice Atelier, you will sit down with our design team to consult with you to develop and create what you have in mind. When you visit Aidan and Ice Atelier, we will walk you through with a variety of crystal, pearl, colored stone, metal and other material options.</p>\r\n<p>Let us help to create and bedazzled your dream piece. Book an appointment with Aidan and Ice Atelier at sales@aidanandice.com or call us at</p>\r\n<p>(+62) 21 7200313.</p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Terms & Conditions',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (19,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,10,'','','Shipping & Exchange Policy',0,'','SHIPPING & EXCHANGE','','<p><strong>NO REFUNDS, NO RETURNS, EXCHANGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>Aidan and Ice’s high quality jewelry should meet or exceed your expectations. However, if you are not completely satisfied with your purchased because of these following reasons:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The products delivered to you are incomplete or manufacturer defect</li>\r\n<li>You have received incorrect products</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We don’t have NO LIABILITY to you unless you inform us at: <a href=\"mailto:sales@aidanandice.com\">sales@aidanandice.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p><b>FOR EXCHANGE</b> the item(s) to the address provided (will be provided in the email) within 2 DAYS of delivery. Please send an email to sales@aidanandice.com regarding the exchange with this following information:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Put &quot;EXCHANGE&quot; on the email subject</li>\r\n<li>Explain the reason why do you need to exchange your item (s)-</li>\r\n<li>Products Information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Aidan and Ice team has the rights to reject your <b>EXCHANGE</b> request. Our Policy:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>All products including exchange item (s) must be in the original condition and accompanied by the original receipt.</li>\r\n<li>Damaged item (s) due to your negligence will not be accepted for refund. Aidan and Ice will not refund the cost of the item unless the item are postage and packed properly.</li>\r\n<li>All requests will be processed after our office inspects and verifies the condition of the Products.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Returns take approximately 3 to 5 business days to process upon receipt of the item.</p>\r\n<p><b>For Exchange:</b> Items can only be exchanged with same value or higher value product. If you wish to exchange your item with higher value item, Aidan and Ice team will calculate the amount of your remaining balance. We will deliver the product immediately after the payment process is completed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>REPAIR POLIC</strong></p>\r\n<p>After two days, if there is any defect on the accessory, client will need to send us the product accompanied by the original receipt, dust bag, and repair form. Please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:sales@aidanandice.com\">sales@aidanandice.com</a> regarding the repair query. After we receive your repair query, we will immediately send you the “Repair Form” for you to fill and please attach the “Repair Form”, dust bag, and the original receipt when you send us the product.</p>\r\n<p>A repair form must be filled in order to indicate the repair query so that Aidan and Ice repairmen team can verify its condition with the actual product. Prior to the repairmen process, Aidan and Ice will inform you the repairmen cost, in which repair charges will be determined per work and materials upon receiving of merchandise. (Client needs to attach any detachment materials from the product because due to our rare materials, Aidan and Ice can’t guarantee the availability of the lost materials.)</p>\r\n<p><b>Product repairmen process takes approximately 4-8 weeks</b></p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Shipping & Exchange',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (20,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,11,'','','Privacy & Policy',0,'','PRIVACY POLICY','','<p>Welcome to the Aidan and Ice Website</p>\r\n<p>At Aidan and Ice we are committed to the protection of your personal information. We’ll always keep your data safe and secure. This policy sets out how we collect, use, manage, transfer, disclose, and store personal information in the course of doing business.</p>\r\n<p>By submitting your information to us, you agree to the processing set out in this Policy.  Further notices highlighting certain uses we wish to make of your personal information together with the ability to opt in or out of selected uses may also be provided to you when we collect personal information from you. For all our services, the data controller – the company that is responsible for your privacy – is aidanandice.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1. Terminology</strong></p>\r\n<p>In this Policy:</p>\r\n<p>\"personal information\" means any information or opinion about a living natural person (whether or not true), including information that can reasonably be used to identify a specific natural person</p>\r\n<p>\"we,\" \"us,\" \"our,\" and \"Aidan and Ice\" are references to Aidan and Ice and</p>\r\n<p>\"you\" and \"your\" means a natural person whose personal information we have collected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. What personal information we collect and how?</strong></p>\r\n<p>As part of our operations we collect personal information. We collect your personal data when you place an order, call our Customer Service team, sign up for our marketing communications, brows our website.  The specific personal information that we may collect or hold will depend on the context in which we collect it, and may include your name, telephone or mobile phone number, addresses, banking details, credit card information, details of transactions you conduct through our website or through other channels and of the fulfillment of your orders, and any other personal information you or a person ostensibly authorized by you submits to us, as well any other information that we consider necessary such as your shopping habits and the pages and products you have viewed from your use of the website.</p>\r\n<p>We collect your personal information in a number of ways,</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Where you provide information directly to us, including through our website or when you participate in promotions run by us</li>\r\n<li>Where you interact directly with our employees and such other persons acting for us or on our behalf such as our customer service team</li>\r\n<li>Where you provide information directly to us during a recruitment process</li>\r\n<li>Through referrals from individuals or other entities</li>\r\n<li>Through marketing and business development events</li>\r\n<li>From related entities in our corporate group; and</li>\r\n<li>From publicly available sources of information</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3. Purpose of collection and use of information</strong></p>\r\n<p>We collect, use and disclose personal information for the primary purpose of conducting our business, which includes:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Deliver your purchases to you</li>\r\n<li>Send you service messages by text, e-mail or through app, such as order updates</li>\r\n<li>Sending information by email, or post about our new products and services.</li>\r\n<li>In the case of potential employees, assessing a person’s application for employment with us, and verifying your details and contacting your references</li>\r\n<li>Researching and assessing our services and products to identify possible improvements, including collecting, using, and disclosing details about your usage patterns and interests</li>\r\n<li>Responding to an inquiry or request</li>\r\n<li>Resolving disputes or addressing complaints</li>\r\n<li>To prevent and detect fraud against either you or Aidan and Ice</li>\r\n<li>Where you otherwise provide your consent, whether express or implied</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4. How information is shared</strong></p>\r\n<p>We do not, and will not, sell any of your personal data to any third party – including your name, address, email address or credit card information. We want to earn and maintain your trust, and we believe this is absolutely essential in order do that. However, we share your data with the following categories of companies as an essential part of being able to provide our services to you, as set out in this statement:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Companies in the Aidan and Ice, as sometimes different bits of our group are responsible for different activities (especially licensed ones)</li>\r\n<li>Companies that do things to get your purchases to you, such as payment service providers, warehouses, order packers, and delivery companies</li>\r\n<li>Professional service providers, such as marketing agencies, advertising partners and website hosts, who help us run our business</li>\r\n<li>Credit reference agencies, law enforcement and fraud prevention agencies, so we can help tackle fraud</li>\r\n<li>Companies approved by you, such as social media sites (if you choose to link your accounts to us), Marketplace sellers where you place an order, and where you choose to use their payment service</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>We may provide third parties with aggregated but anonymized information and analytics about our customers and, before we do so, we will make sure that it does not identify you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5. Storage, security, and retention of personal information</strong></p>\r\n<p>Where we hold your personal information, we will take reasonable steps to ensure that the information is secure and may only be accessed by authorized persons. Where we store your personal information electronically on our database, we use secure servers and there are restrictions as to who has access to that information through password protection. All hardcopies of personal information are stored in secure areas.  Please notify us immediately if you believe there has been any unauthorized access to your information.</p>\r\n<p>Although we take reasonable steps, we do not control how a third-party partner may use your data. Please note that third party recipients of personal information may have their own privacy policies and we are not responsible for their actions, including their handling of personal information.</p>\r\n<p>We keep personal information as long as it is reasonably necessary for the purposes described in this Policy or otherwise in compliance with our or our service providers’ data retention policies.  Certain information may be retained until the time limit for any legal challenges has expired or in order to comply with regulatory requirements regarding the retention of such personal information.  If you have provided us with personal information in the course of applying for employment with us, and your application has not been successful, we may keep your personal information in case a suitable role becomes available.  Where applicable, if any personal information that we hold is no longer required for the purpose for which it was collected and no applicable law requires us to retain that information, we will take reasonable steps to de-identify or destroy the information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6. Accessing, updating, and deleting your information</strong></p>\r\n<p>We will take reasonable steps to ensure the personal information we hold is complete, up to date and accurate, so far as it is practicable for us to do so.</p>\r\n<p>Applicable data protection laws may give you the right to access, correct, or delete personal information that we hold   about you.  You may request to access or correct the personal information we hold about you by contacting our Privacy Officer.  Please see the contact details below.  We will comply with our obligations to provide you with access to your personal information and to correct any inaccuracies we are informed of in accordance with applicable data protection laws.</p>\r\n<p>Data subjects whose processing is based upon consent may withdraw that consent at any time; however, we will not be able to provide or continue to provide services or marketing communications to the data subject.  Please make request to withdraw consent pursuant to the instructions above.</p>\r\n<p>When we ask for information from you, you are given the opportunity to ‘opt-in’ to receive additional information, such as site announcements, product reviews, promotional information, product sampling opportunities and research requests from us and to allow us to share your contact information with certain of our trusted partners and customers. Users who no longer wish to receive these communications, or who do not want their contact information shared as described herein, may stop receiving them by following the Unsubscribe instructions included in any communication or by following the Access procedures above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>7. Direct marketing</strong></p>\r\n<p>From time to time, we may use your personal information for direct marketing purposes (for an indefinite period).  Where required by law, we will ask for your consent before conducting any of these types of marketing.  This includes sending you updates about our products and offerings. When we contact you, it may be by mail, telephone, email or SMS. Where we use or disclose your personal information for the purpose of direct marketing, we will:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Inform you if we intend to use your information for such purposes</li>\r\n<li>Allow you to ‘opt out’ or, in other words, allow you to request not to receive direct marketing communications; and</li>\r\n<li>Comply with any such request by you to ‘opt-out’ of receiving further communications within a reasonable time frame.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>We will provide an option to unsubscribe or opt-out of further communication on any electronic marketing communication sent to you.  You may ask to be removed from our marketing lists at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link or by directly contacting us.  If you don\'t wish to receive direct marketing materials, contact our Privacy Officer using the details set out at the end of this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8. Questions and complaints</strong></p>\r\n<p>Aidan and Ice is the data controller in respect of your personal information under this Policy,</p>\r\n<p>If you have a question about how we handle personal information, or wish to lodge a complaint about our management   of personal information (including if you believe that we have managed your personal information in breach of applicable privacy laws), you may contact our Privacy Officer:</p>\r\n<p>Attention: Privacy Officer Aidan and Ice <br>\r\nAddress: Jl. Taman Mpu Sendok No. 27 Kebayoran Baru, Jakarta 12190 Indonesia  <br>\r\nEmail: hello@aidanandice.com<br>\r\nTelephone: +6221 7200313 </p>\r\n<p>The Privacy Officer will co-ordinate the investigation of any complaint and any potential resolution of a complaint. In order to be sure that we understand the details and nature of your question or complaint, we may ask you to put your question or complaint in writing. We will aim to resolve all complaints as soon as practicable for us to do so</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>9. Changes to this Policy</strong></p>\r\n<p>We may change this Policy at any time. Please refer back to this Policy periodically to review any updates. If we make material changes to this Policy we will notify you by publication on our website. The revised version of the Policy will be effective at the time we post it, which time will be indicated at the end of this Policy. You agree to be bound by any modified or amended versions of this Policy.</p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,1,1,1,'','Super Admin','Footer','','Privacy Policy',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (21,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,12,'','','Career Section',0,'','BE A PART OF AIDAN & ICE TEAM','','<p>We\'re looking for highly motivated, happy people to be apart of our ever-growing team! If you think you have what it takes, send your cover letter and resume to <a href=\"mailto:hello@aidanandice.com\">hello@aidanandice.com</a></p>','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,0,1,0,1,1,'1920px x 660px','Super Admin','Footer','','Join Our Team',0,'');");
		$this->db->simple_query("INSERT INTO `section`(`id`,`created`,`updated`,`deletable`,`editable`,`author_id`,`header_id`,`type`,`number`,`name`,`date`,`status`,`title`,`subtitle`,`description`,`custom_text_1`,`custom_text_2`,`link`,`name_lang`,`title_lang`,`subtitle_lang`,`description_lang`,`custom_text_1_lang`,`custom_text_2_lang`,`no_name`,`no_title`,`no_subtitle`,`no_description`,`no_link`,`no_image`,`no_custom_text_1`,`no_custom_text_2`,`image_size`,`author_name`,`header_type`,`header_number`,`header_name`,`header_date`,`header_status`) VALUES (22,'2000-01-01 00:00:00','2000-01-01 00:00:00',0,0,1,13,'','','CONTACT US SECTION',0,'','CONTACT US','','','','','','','','','','','',1,0,1,1,1,0,1,1,'1920px x 660px','Super Admin','Footer','','Contact Us',0,'');");

		$this->db->simple_query("CREATE TABLE `slideshow` (
		  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
		  `created` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
		  `updated` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
